<h4>Hosts</h4>

<p>Here you list all your monitored hosts, edit them and add new ones.</p>

<h5>List hosts</h5>
<p>Shows all you configured hosts, their number of monitored services and their IP addresses.</p>

<h5>Add new host / Edit host</h5>
<p><b>Hostname</b>: short name to identify the host (cannot be changed after initial creation).</p>
<p><b>Alias</b>: longer name or description of the host (can be changed afterwards).</p>
